Uses of Package
org.activebpel.rt

Packages that use org.activebpel.rt
org.activebpel.rt Globally useful runtime classes and interfaces.  
org.activebpel.rt.attachment   
org.activebpel.rt.axis Root package for the Active Endpoints Runtime for Axis (rtaxis).  
org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel Root package for the Active Endpoints Runtime for Axis (rtaxis).  
org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.deploy Root package for the Active Endpoints Axis specific deployment code. 
org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.handlers Handlers translate between messages and protocol formats such as JAX-RPC or SOAP Document.  
org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.invokers Contains impls of the actual rpc or document style invokers used to call out to external web services.  
org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.rdebug.server Contains all server module for the ActiveBPEL remote administration and debug Web Services. 
org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.web Provides servlet entry point into the ActiveBPEL engine.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel This package contains classes for creating a BPEL model and for implements a standalone BPEL engine for testing designs. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.config This package contains the base classes for configuring the BPEL engine.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.coord This package contains the base classes for implementing coordination. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def This package contains base classes and elements used to create BPEL model definitions. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.activity This package contains classes which define the various BPEL activities. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.activity.support This package contains classes which support various BPEL activities.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.expr This package contains base classes and elements used for expression handling.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.expr.xpath This package contains implementation classes for an expression parser and analyzer for xpath language.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.ext This package contains the classes for reading and writing extension elements for BPEL.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.readers This package contains the default impl of the IAeBpelReader interface.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.readers.def This package contains the IAeBpelDefReader interface for reading in BPEL xml and the default impls. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.registry This package contains the registry classes for accessing readers and writers for BPEL and extension elements.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.writers This package provides the impl classes for the IAeBpelWriter interface.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.writers.def This package contains the IAeBpelDefWriter interface for serializing specific AeBaseDef object subclasses and the default impls. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.expr This package contains classes which support validation of expressions. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.expressions This package contains validation model implementation classes for expression based validation. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.query This package contains validation model implementation classes for query related validation. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors Classes implementing the Visitor pattern used to perform various functions on the activity definitions.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.expr   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.ext.expr.def.javascript This package contains implementation classes for an expression parser and analyzer for the javascript language.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.ext.expr.def.xquery This package contains implementation classes for an expression parser and analyzer for xquery language.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.function   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl This package contains the base classes used in the implementation model for the BPEL activities. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.assign This package contains implementation objects used for executing the assign activity. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.support Includes supporting bpel objects which aren't properly activities.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.expr This package contains classes which support running expressions. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.function   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.lock Locking facility used to control access to variables when there are serializable scopes in the process.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.reply   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.storage Classes related to saving and restoring the state of processes.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.addressing Handles partner addressing (finding the correct endpoint reference for a given business partner).  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.addressing.pdef Handles partner definitions and addressing across all BPEL processes.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.admin Classes that manage queued receives and a bean that holds deployed process information.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.admin.rdebug.server   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.catalog   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.catalog.report This package contains the Catalog reporting (console) support classes. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.catalog.resource This package contains the resource catalog, its associated interfaces and helper classes. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy Process deployment.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy.bpr Loading and reading BPR deployment archives during process deployment.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy.scanner Active directory scanning facilities.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy.validate Root package for the Active Endpoints BPEL Deployment Validation code.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine The BPEL engine, support classes, and engine factory.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.invoke   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.receive   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.recovery This package contains classes for recovering or regenerating the state of a process from alarms, messages, or faults that the process received. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.recovery.journal This package contains classes for representing journal entries for alarms, messages, or faults for possible recovery in the event of engine failure. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.recovery.test This package contains classes for testing the functionality of the recovery engine. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.reply   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage This package contains classes for storing the state of BPEL processes to an external storage facility. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.exist   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.sql This package contains classes for storing the state of BPEL processes to a SQL database. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.sql.debug   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.sql.upgrade   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.tamino Contains classes and interfaces that form the base implementation of Tamino database support.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.tamino.installer Contains a command-line application used to install/define a Tamino schema into a running Tamino database.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.xmldb Contains classes and interfaces that form the base implementation of XMLDB database support.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.xmldb.process Contains the storage classes that implement a XMLDB version of the Process storage.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.transaction   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.security   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.transreceive This package contains the transmission tracker and it's related classes.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.wsdl This package contains the WSDL helpers for resolving wsdl entries through the catalog. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.xpath.ast This package contains the base classes for implementing a Jaxen based XPath Abstract Syntax Tree.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.graph This package contains bean classes used by the active bpel WAR.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.graph.ui This package contains bean classes used by the active bpel WAR.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.web This package contains java beans and supporting classes for driving the web app ui. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.web.graph   
org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.web.processview This package contains all the code and presentation beans for driving the web app Process Details view ui. 
org.activebpel.rt.config   
org.activebpel.rt.message The interface and class used to manage WSDL message data.  
org.activebpel.rt.util Utility classes for XML handling, reading JARs, I/O, and a blocking queue.  
org.activebpel.rt.war.tags This package contains all the custom tags used for driving the web app ui. 
org.activebpel.rt.wsdl A factory for loading WSDL files that may be cached locally.  
org.activebpel.rt.wsdl.def Classes that represent WSDL elements (partner links, port types, properties, and the like) and that serialize and deserialize them.  
org.activebpel.rt.wsdl.def.policy   
org.activebpel.rt.xml Package which contains runtime components used by Active Endpoints plugins.  
org.activebpel.rt.xml.schema   
org.activebpel.rt.xml.schema.sampledata.util   
org.activebpel.work.factory The factory that provides the CommonJ WorkManager and the IAeInputMessageWorkManager (input message work manager) to the engine.
